    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "A I agents can write. They can talk. They can code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6be6b012392c7b6444c51d3c292b6f666733c467314ab24574f1c57222acadb6",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "They operate autonomously. But one thing has stayed just out of reach.",
      "checksum": "sha256:28bed1b79f3f1b74f2b20d35e0ef17fa17ff750598f7f20182610ea6556851b3",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Editing video. HeyGen open-sourced HyperFrames to fix that.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9f8d4fcf7d1913704ae7281072c45464bf9c601e63030f3e4605b4a4574e7355",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 23
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "And here's the kicker. This entire video was made by Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6a373bbd8de5ce5b1ac43851539ce61e61c82bc906da95109d3a5d7ee346650d",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 31
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Using HyperFrames itself. Every video tool today has the same flaw.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4a41f2a972a2178b6f4daefa2f6e1ce27df24830151d3fef6aa3bd7e8b9ac7d8",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "After Effects. DaVinci Resolve. Premiere.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eaee6fd8248ad882c7ba941530a6d6fe22b20c906059d98fb82e722918b1ce7a",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 54
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "They are all built on JSON or X M L timelines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7e788fb4a2ac8b45ce1a59665f36f509391de7e393a88e033baf83c0631a7204",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 59
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Layers. Keyframes. Years of human muscle memory.",
      "checksum": "sha256:911002c7348d68f631874f8398853c8251e50d6a2d0f60db425887750f94ff24",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 70
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "None of that lives in agent training data.",
      "checksum": "sha256:30dc5ae9f022d769f413bbd703b5887604e237f1ddee044bed254aa88624d2f0",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 77
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "So agents stumble. Every time. The toolchain was the bottleneck.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f1425f8b8875e463454eb78da594374adde188b16c3bf4c72233eea9e6afd73f",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Now look at what agents do know. They were trained on the entire web.",
      "checksum": "sha256:efe7baadeaa23c7293115e4e0f611df99a59833378f9a4c2c3b09fc7f6bc8cba",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Billions of H T M L pages. Millions of C S S and JavaScript animations.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de6effe493bc0e89a83833a71c9befb0c5d45954c1009b3e910107cc93cbf66b",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 109
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Hundreds of thousands of G S A P snippets, S V G compositions, and canvas experiments.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c15689604d40b9b2e9e59811864f8d8bb1fbf8cfcbcd35b5298cd78d5ef586c1",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The web is the largest creative medium in their training data, by orders of magnitude.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9662507a96f90de7dcaa09d2872c8b3f6bc413961d8ee446ba4e4b184ae9d443",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "H T M L is their native tongue. So HyperFrames takes their best work, and adds a thin layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7d24d8d0d932a17f24bfe2ac897817095bda7721c382505dc99cda90726128b2",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 5.897868480725624,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 155
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Three data attributes. data start. data duration. data track index.",
      "checksum": "sha256:715ff8cfc702e506b76ca1e75a890fc8042c4e5f28713a73d867c465fc7e9a9c",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 174
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "That's it. Add them to any H T M L element and you have a video timeline.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8a607501e7dbb60a6e12c1712f1107841f516f0e8a789a30cbf1b10242783e18",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 184
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "The agent writes regular H T M L, C S S, and JavaScript.",
      "checksum": "sha256:723243025a78964f09f019316b4078c5a733b86f821b6ded8c546ddef1bc9de3",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 201
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "HyperFrames turns it into M P 4. Or M O V.",
      "checksum": "sha256:deccfeca9a17bbdca7ea992aa507253d1f6a715bf50d69194c1511ee09f2fca7",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 214
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Or web M. And here's the part that breaks people's brains.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ee3c1f15f696a32f95f48db67d50fe4f424baa4965808e9df08a0222e98aec0c",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 225
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Anything that works in a browser, works in HyperFrames.",
      "checksum": "sha256:684ebfb63c557ee53a33147ac84fc56cfff0c0502b9e5aee7b72ed8ab374c7e6",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 236
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "C S S animations. G S A P timelines. Lottie.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f6c744429c038ecb2d2e670a7b0c01d118e763f93f39aa14f105a024504df1e9",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 245
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Three dot J S. D 3 visualizations. Google Fonts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cf7df54ae91897212c8c56f80ae6500dd2190b567cb22261211bc37ab136f118",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 255
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Whatever the agent already knows from the open web, it can use directly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52acf1195a672a254e42ec45d1a4edb7b39136464eecddf15c7bb21879a4e074",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 264
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "No wrappers. No framework to learn. For a long time, the models weren't quite there.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4505e6e7f54cdced8791236feb59405b08fbbe6906addedacd7521184cc94ab",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 277
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Code generation worked, but quality wasn't reliable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:159c57a4488f0a5e83cb7cecff1029b37f8b53f553d341ce233a6b7c3d712d02",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 292
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Then November 2025 happened. Gemini 3 and Opus 4 point 5 previewed. HeyGen swapped them in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:80bfa94b25c1bfea3d98532752d490ef8b0372dff836a3ba749dfbcc8e5d4586",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 299
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "And the agent started producing motion graphics and multi-scene B rolls.",
      "checksum": "sha256:490bf1d9d57a6fa8a6b3531c7404e048e1e8499102d809230337c36ff20689d5",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 315
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Consistently. With high quality. That was the moment HyperFrames converged.\n\nHyperFrames is open source.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0c732f8abd2bb9e07678ef151c2deeb33c5d49970500cf7b0ba25ef0963fb447",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 6.222947845804988,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Apache 2 point 0. One command turns any agent into a video editor.",
      "checksum": "sha256:220c1240e59d260801ba03033b67b5081b6b870a3d7f1b4cd71274e2cbc7d733",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.690430839002268,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 340
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "N P X skills add heygen-com slash hyperframes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0d037d2f4281c1f181fb0641e9242d4ccc9a44f6516ba8f010fa74c339039f3b",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 353
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Point your agent at the skill. Hand it a topic.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3aed5c470ed886996f720831e43aa961d338b669ff21650084a3926d92569b34",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 361
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "And watch it write a video. So tell me. HyperFrames.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f931c38b31d141013f499aad483915f2f0cf17437fc11063960b08b8c4c92a2c",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 371
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Remotion. Or Motion Canvas. Which one are you shipping with.",
      "checksum": "sha256:23f5dd4e661172bf9783544fdef8ec3bcf344fdf9e65622ad8d3b956ee17968b",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 381
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Comment your pick below.",
      "checksum": "sha256:97b66a6bcba75e5a2d3268712a76929703e6f2dd764f229a1fd3917055088dc7",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 1.3467573696145125,
      "word_count": 4,
      "words_offset": 391
    }
  ]
}